153
00:11:12,660 --> 00:11:15,750
Aku ini Kesatria Sihir, lo!

154
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,870
Meskipun harus mati,
aku takkan sudi melakukannya!

155
00:11:19,130 --> 00:11:24,300
Dan sampai aku jadi Kaisar Sihir,
aku takkan mati.

156
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:26,420
Asta, di sebelah kananmu.

157
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:27,220
Gawat.

158
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:31,470
Padahal kau berteriak takkan
mati seperti orang bodoh,

159
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:33,350
